<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Test de aptitud mental OTIS</title>
    
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- CSS link -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/aspirantes/pruebaOtis.css">
    
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container mt-4">
        <h2 class="text-center">Test de aptitud mental OTIS</h2>
        <hr>

        <!-- Datos Personales -->
        <h5>Datos personales</h5>
        <hr>
        <div class="row gx-3 mb-3">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Nombre">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Apellido Paterno">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Apellido Materno">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row gx-3 mb-3">
            <div class="col-md-2">
                <input type="number" class="form-control" placeholder="Edad">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <select class="form-select">
                    <option>Género</option>
                    <option>Masculino</option>
                    <option>Femenino</option>
                    <option>No binario</option>
                    <option>Prefiero no decirlo</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <select class="form-select">
                    <option>Escolaridad</option>
                    <option>Licenciatura</option>
                    <option>Maestría</option>
                    <option>Doctorado</option>
                    <option>Otro</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Puesto solicitado">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Seccion de preguntas -->
        <h5>Preguntas</h5>
        <hr>
        
        <!-- Preguntas de la prueba OTIS -->
        <div class="mb-3">
            <p><strong>1. El opuesto de amor es.....?</strong></p>
            <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q1"><label class="form-check-label">1. grado</label></div>
            <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q1"><label class="form-check-label">2. enojo</label></div>
            <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q1"><label class="form-check-label">3. odio</label></div>
            <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q1"><label class="form-check-label">4. extraño</label></div>
            <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q1"><label class="form-check-label">5. novio</label></div>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-3">
            <p><strong>2. Decir que las piedras piensan es.....?</strong></p>
            <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q2"><label class="form-check-label">1. absurdo</label></div>
            <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q2"><label class="form-check-label">2. engañoso</label></div>
            <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q2"><label class="form-check-label">3. improbable</label></div>
            <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q2"><label class="form-check-label">4. injusto</label></div>
            <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q2"><label class="form-check-label">5. malo</label></div>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-3">
            <p><strong>3. El oro vale más que la plata porque es.....?</strong></p>
            <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q3"><label class="form-check-label">1. más pesado</label></div>
            <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q3"><label class="form-check-label">2. más escaso</label></div>
            <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q3"><label class="form-check-label">3. más amarillo</label></div>
            <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q3"><label class="form-check-label">4. más duro</label></div>
            <div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q3"><label class="form-check-label">5. más hermoso</label></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Boton finalizar -->
        <div class="text-end mt-4">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-color--secondary" onclick="window.location.href='/Aspirante/mis-pruebas'">Terminar</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
